00:02:07,820 --> 00:02:08,220
Mr. Ge.

5
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:08,550
Hello.

6
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:09,100
Hello.

7
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:10,550
I'm Ge Qing.

8
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:11,990
The characters used
for kudzu root and the color green.

9
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:13,790
How do you do?

10
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:15,300
Please sit.

11
00:02:15,350 --> 00:02:15,820
Okay.

12
00:02:16,100 --> 00:02:16,630
Thank you.

13
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:18,270
Take your time.

14
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:20,070
Be careful.

15
