459
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,650
What's this?

460
00:17:23,650 --> 00:17:25,200
Research data of the research group.

461
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,400
Does that mean

462
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,440
you're very satisfied

