00:30:43,010 --> 00:30:44,490
in our hospital.

865
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:47,010
Didn't you say you trusted him?

866
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:51,730
Dr. Ruan,

867
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:53,850
have you seen Dr. Ning smile before?

868
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:58,560
I've seen him smile in the past.

869
00:30:58,800 --> 00:30:59,970
I rarely see it now.

870
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:03,320
I'm curious

871
00:31:04,010 --> 00:31:05,610
what he looks like when he smiles.

872
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:07,130
Why?

873
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:11,010
I joined the dance team at a young age.

874
00:31:11,770 --> 00:31:12,920
I have no parents.

875
00:31:13,850 --> 00:31:15,370
Other kids always picked on me.

876
00:31:17,010 --> 00:31:18,440
Only one big brother

877
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,770
always took care of me

878
00:31:20,770 --> 00:31:21,680
and was concerned about me.

879
00:31:23,010 --> 00:31:24,730
He danced very well.

880
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:26,850
He's the pillar of our team.

881
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,730
But too bad

882
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:32,370
he was transferred to another troupe.

883
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,610
I never saw him again.

884
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:37,610
Guess what, Dr. Ruan.

885
00:31:38,130 --> 00:31:40,040
Dr. Ning looks similar to him.

886
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:43,610
So whenever I see Dr. Ning,

887
00:31:43,770 --> 00:31:45,400
I feel particularly close to him.

888
00:31:47,490 --> 00:31:49,730
But he always treats me coldly.

889
00:31:50,440 --> 00:31:51,800
That's what he's like.

890
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:52,970
Don't take it personally.

891
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:54,490
He doesn't do that to you alone.

892
00:31:54,490 --> 00:31:56,400
He's cold to everyone.

893
00:31:57,250 --> 00:31:57,970
Really?

894
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,770
I thought he hated me.

895
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:02,130
Of course, not.

896
00:32:04,730 --> 00:32:05,800
Oh, Dr. Ruan.

897
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:07,850
Can you do me a favor?

898
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:08,680
What is it?

899
00:32:10,130 --> 00:32:11,090
I know

900
00:32:11,090 --> 00:32:12,970
I'll lose my hair from chemotherapy.

901
00:32:13,890 --> 00:32:14,560
So

902
00:32:14,890 --> 00:32:16,370
can you take a picture of me?

903
00:32:19,010 --> 00:32:19,650
Sure.

904
00:32:20,010 --> 00:32:20,920
Give me your phone.

905
00:32:22,090 --> 00:32:22,850
It's in the drawer.

906
00:32:29,250 --> 00:32:30,010
Smile.

907
00:32:36,970 --> 00:32:38,010
Thank you, Dr. Ruan.

908
00:32:38,490 --> 00:32:40,200
Do you feel any discomfort?

909
00:32:40,320 --> 00:32:41,090
Does it hurt?

910
00:32:41,090 --> 00:32:41,730
Do it slowly.

911
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,010
Relax.

912
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:50,490
Repeat what you said just now.

913
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:51,440
I said,

914
00:32:51,560 --> 00:32:53,440
can you visit Du Xiaoyu

915
00:32:53,730 --> 00:32:54,800
and smile for him?

916
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,490
I'm a doctor, not an entertainer.

917
00:32:56,560 --> 00:32:57,320
It's something

918
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,800
you can do pretty easily.

919
00:32:59,010 --> 00:33:00,610
Can you say something nice

920
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:01,280
to lighten him up

921
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:02,090
and comfort him?

922
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:03,160
It's not that hard.

923
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,610
I'm sorry. I can't do it.

924
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,320
Mr. Ning,

925
00:33:07,010 --> 00:33:08,250
you know about Du Xiaoyu's condition

926
00:33:08,250 --> 00:33:09,520
more than I do.

927
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:11,520
The tumor on his brain stem

928
00:33:11,520 --> 00:33:12,920
is probably the most malignant

929
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,010
glioblastoma.

930
00:33:14,130 --> 00:33:15,560
He'll die if he doesn't do the surgery.

931
00:33:15,890 --> 00:33:17,160
The prognosis is not ideal even
after we remove the tumor.

932
00:33:17,370 --> 00:33:18,680
In his case,

933
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,680
his five-year survival rate
is less than five percent.

934
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:23,250
So?

935
00:33:23,370 --> 00:33:24,770
So I hope he has a better time

936
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:25,730
in the hospital.

937
00:33:26,090 --> 00:33:26,970
Dr. Ruan,

938
00:33:27,320 --> 00:33:29,130
your job is not
to make the patient happy,

939
00:33:29,610 --> 00:33:30,970
but to cure him.

940
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:32,090
So he can keep living.

941
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,440
What's the difference?

942
00:33:33,650 --> 00:33:34,730
I'll say this one more time.

943
00:33:35,010 --> 00:33:36,090
You must keep your distance

944
00:33:36,090 --> 00:33:37,200
from the patients as far as possible.

945
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,200
Why?

946
00:33:38,490 --> 00:33:39,850
It helps you
to be objective and rational

947
00:33:39,850 --> 00:33:41,010
as a doctor.

948
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:52,520
Oh, my. You're all grown up.

949
00:33:52,770 --> 00:33:53,920
When I first saw you,

950
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:54,970
you were just this small.

951
00:33:55,090 --> 00:33:57,130
You're now this tall in a flash.

952
00:33:57,650 --> 00:33:58,730
Come with me.

953
00:33:58,730 --> 00:33:59,320
Come.

954
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:01,160
Time sure flies.

955
00:34:02,770 --> 00:34:04,160
Let's play another round.

956
00:34:04,650 --> 00:34:06,010
Your dad and I

957
00:34:06,370 --> 00:34:07,280
are equally skilled

958
00:34:07,280 --> 00:34:08,040
and capable opponents in chess.

959
00:34:08,090 --> 00:34:09,240
Neither one of us would give in.

960
00:34:09,240 --> 00:34:10,610
Xue, have some drinks.

961
00:34:10,610 --> 00:34:11,560
Thank you, Madam.

962
00:34:12,240 --> 00:34:13,170
When my dad has free time,

963
00:34:13,170 --> 00:34:14,280
he always makes me play chess with him.

964
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,090
What did I tell you?

965
00:34:15,090 --> 00:34:16,170
Let's play one round.

966
00:34:16,210 --> 00:34:16,450
Come.

967
00:34:16,450 --> 00:34:16,760
Okay.

968
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:17,410
I'll go first.

969
00:34:17,410 --> 00:34:17,930
You can go first.

970
00:34:18,170 --> 00:34:18,850
I'll move the Elephant.

971
00:34:19,650 --> 00:34:20,130
Say,

972
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:22,090
he has such a handsome face
and he's a lawyer too.

973
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:23,320
He sure does.

974
00:34:23,930 --> 00:34:25,370
Dad. Mom, I'm home.

975
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:26,850
Dr. Ruan, you're back.

976
00:34:27,850 --> 00:34:28,520
Mr. Xue,

977
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,130
what are you doing here?

978
00:34:29,370 --> 00:34:30,760
I happened to be working nearby.

979
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,000
So I dropped by to visit your parents.

980
00:34:34,170 --> 00:34:34,760
Sit down.

981
00:34:36,410 --> 00:34:37,040
Xue,

982
00:34:37,210 --> 00:34:38,240
go and sit on the sofa.

983
00:34:38,890 --> 00:34:39,890
We're in the middle
of playing chess here.

984
00:34:39,890 --> 00:34:40,650
Stop playing

985
00:34:40,690 --> 00:34:41,280
for a while.

986
00:34:41,450 --> 00:34:42,520
Xue, take a seat.

987
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,520
Then I'll continue the game
with you later.

988
00:34:44,560 --> 00:34:46,090
Okay, go and take a seat.

989
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,370
They look good together.

990
00:34:51,890 --> 00:34:52,800
What do you mean?

991
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:53,800
They look good together.

992
00:35:01,690 --> 00:35:02,240
Shall we talk

993
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,480
about the case?

994
00:35:06,130 --> 00:35:06,720
Let's talk outside.

995
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:07,690
Follow me.

996
00:35:09,370 --> 00:35:10,960
Come back for dinner, okay?

997
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,370
Okay. Mr. and Mrs. Ruan,

998
00:35:12,370 --> 00:35:13,170
we'll be heading out.

999
00:35:13,170 --> 00:35:14,210
- Okay. Come back early.
- Okay.

1000
00:35:14,210 --> 00:35:15,040
Come back early.

1001
00:35:22,170 --> 00:35:22,760
The court

1002
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:23,800
has filed your case.

1003
00:35:24,090 --> 00:35:25,210
Thank you so much.

1004
00:35:25,210 --> 00:35:27,130
You're really efficient.

1005
00:35:27,130 --> 00:35:28,560
I don't like dragging things

1006
00:35:28,610 --> 00:35:30,000
when I do something.

1007
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,450
Dr. Ruan,

1008
00:35:31,450 --> 00:35:32,560
you can wait for my good news.

1009
00:35:33,890 --> 00:35:34,650
Who's that?

1010
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,480
Let me introduce you guys.

1011
00:35:36,850 --> 00:35:37,850
This is my brother, Ruan Lang.

1012
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,320
This is Mr. Xue,

1013
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,130
my friend.

1014
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:41,090
Hello.

1015
00:35:41,690 --> 00:35:42,720
I'm Xue Weilin.

1016
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:45,760
I've never heard

1017
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,000
of him before.

1018
00:35:50,930 --> 00:35:52,000
Dr. Ruan and I

1019
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:52,800
only met not too long ago.

1020
00:35:53,130 --> 00:35:54,130
You only met not long ago.

1021
00:35:54,560 --> 00:35:55,610
But you already chased her
all the way home.

1022
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,960
Don't you think you have no manners?

1023
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:00,800
Ruan Lang,

1024
00:36:02,040 --> 00:36:02,800
Mr. Xue

1025
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,800
is the son of Uncle Xue,

1026
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,890
our dad's good friend.

1027
00:36:05,170 --> 00:36:06,410
Our families are old friends.

1028
00:36:08,370 --> 00:36:09,280
So Dad introduced him to you?

1029
00:36:10,410 --> 00:36:12,000
Since when is he this nosy?

1030
00:36:15,130 --> 00:36:16,450
It's getting late.

1031
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,450
I should go back first.

1032
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:18,720
I'll see you off.

1033
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,480
Mr. Xue,

1034
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,000
it's pretty late.

1035
00:36:25,130 --> 00:36:27,320
If my sister sees you off,

1036
00:36:27,370 --> 00:36:28,320
she'll have to walk back home alone.

1037
00:36:28,370 --> 00:36:29,000
It's pretty dangerous.

1038
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:29,930
Otherwise,

1039
00:36:29,930 --> 00:36:31,210
I'll have to go and pick her up.

1040
00:36:31,890 --> 00:36:33,210
How about both of us see you off?

1041
00:36:34,450 --> 00:36:35,210
It's okay.

1042
00:36:36,610 --> 00:36:37,280
I'll get going then.

1043
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:38,890
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

1044
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:40,690
We won't walk you then.

1045
00:36:44,210 --> 00:36:45,930
A gentleman never uses violence.

1046
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:48,480
What was wrong with you?

1047
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:50,650
Yes, something is wrong with me.

1048
00:36:51,090 --> 00:36:52,210
Please send me to the hospital.

1049
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,040
I want to find my brother-in-law.

1050
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,480
Can't you get over it?

1051
00:36:54,610 --> 00:36:56,130
Remember when I say this.

1052
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:57,240
I, Ruan Lang,

1053
00:36:58,690 --> 00:37:00,320
have only one brother-in-law.

1054
00:37:00,650 --> 00:37:01,690
He's Ning Zhiqian.

1055
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:02,890
What?

1056
00:37:03,240 --> 00:37:04,520
Is he a leader of some cult

1057
00:37:04,520 --> 00:37:05,520
that brainwashed you to this extent?

1058
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,480
Liuzheng, you don't get it, do you?

1059
00:37:07,930 --> 00:37:09,650
Men are very mysterious creatures.

1060
00:37:09,930 --> 00:37:11,320
What's the name of the guy
we met just now?

1061
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,170
His name is Xue Weilin.

1062
00:37:14,210 --> 00:37:15,170
Just his name alone sounds

1063
00:37:15,370 --> 00:37:16,450
like Hypocritical Lin.
[*Hypocritical: rhymes with Xue Weilin]

1064
00:37:17,130 --> 00:37:18,040
He just wants to fool around with you.

1065
00:37:18,090 --> 00:37:19,170
I can see right through him.

1066
00:37:20,210 --> 00:37:20,930
Listen.

1067
00:37:20,930 --> 00:37:22,090
Stop overthinking.

1068
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,800
He's helping me with a lawsuit now.

1069
00:37:23,850 --> 00:37:24,760
Don't get the wrong idea.

1070
00:37:24,890 --> 00:37:25,960
That proved I was right.

1071
00:37:26,890 --> 00:37:29,130
He'll take the lawsuit as his chance

1072
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,130
to fool around with you.

1073
00:37:31,690 --> 00:37:32,210
It's over once he gets what he wants.

1074
00:37:32,210 --> 00:37:32,890
Shut up.

1075
00:37:36,690 --> 00:37:37,610
Hello?

1076
00:37:38,450 --> 00:37:39,280
Bank?

1077
00:37:39,690 --> 00:37:41,320
Yes, I've been driving the car.

1078
00:37:45,370 --> 00:37:47,280
What?

1079
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:48,890
Stop it, Liuzheng.

1080
00:37:48,890 --> 00:37:49,520
I'm busy.

1081
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:50,610
Zero down payment?

1082
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:51,610
Cut it out.

1083
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:53,210
How much is it a month?

1084
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:55,520
What? 5900 yuan?

1085
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,090
Dad.

1086
00:37:56,090 --> 00:37:56,610
What are you doing?

1087
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,170
Stop picking on your sister.

1088
00:37:58,170 --> 00:37:59,240
I wasn't picking on her.

1089
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:00,650
I'm teaching her how to dance.

1090
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:07,610
What were you guys doing?

1091
00:38:10,410 --> 00:38:11,280
What did you do?

1092
00:38:22,610 --> 00:38:23,850
Liuzheng, why can't you understand

1093
00:38:23,890 --> 00:38:25,210
my good intention?

1094
00:38:25,690 --> 00:38:27,650
I wanted you to save some time

1095
00:38:27,650 --> 00:38:28,850
so you can tend to more patients

1096
00:38:28,850 --> 00:38:30,320
and learn more knowledge.

1097
00:38:31,130 --> 00:38:31,800
Apart from that,

1098
00:38:32,370 --> 00:38:34,040
I showed them your photo.

1099
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,560
So a beautiful woman like you

1100
00:38:35,610 --> 00:38:36,450
deserved a zero down payment

1101
00:38:36,450 --> 00:38:37,040
and a discount.

1102
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,610
It's a limited edition,

1103
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:40,890
which matches you.

1104
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:43,560
Stop right there.

1105
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,000
You can let me trick you.

1106
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:49,450
But don't let other men do the same.

1107
00:38:50,850 --> 00:38:51,480
Listen here!

1108
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:52,760
Don't meddle in my affairs.

1109
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:55,960
If I don't, would you grow up like this?

1110
00:38:56,450 --> 00:38:57,720
I wasn't talking to you.

1111
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:00,610
Unbelievable.

1112
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,450
What's the matter?

1113
00:39:20,450 --> 00:39:21,370
I could hear

1114
00:39:21,370 --> 00:39:22,720
you acting mischievous from outside.

1115
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:23,890
Why are you still awake, brat?

1116
00:39:23,890 --> 00:39:24,760
Stop playing around.

1117
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:25,240
Come here!

1118
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,760
Sleep with me.

1119
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,650
- Or else I
- I can't sleep.

1120
00:39:28,690 --> 00:39:29,690
- won't sleep.
- I need to work.

1121
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:30,480
Go to bed.

1122
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,650
If you don't sleep with me,

1123
00:39:31,650 --> 00:39:32,800
I'll stay awake.

1124
00:39:33,210 --> 00:39:34,000
Dad,

1125
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:35,370
Mom

1126
00:39:35,690 --> 00:39:37,320
hasn't come for days.

1127
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:39,890
Is she going on blind dates again?

1128
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:42,520
She has been busy working these days.

1129
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:43,040
So she has no free time.

1130
00:39:43,410 --> 00:39:44,650
Even if she doesn't go on blind dates,

1131
00:39:44,650 --> 00:39:46,040
what if another man

1132
00:39:46,040 --> 00:39:47,410
goes after her?

1133
00:39:48,890 --> 00:39:50,170
That's not likely to happen.

1134
00:39:50,170 --> 00:39:51,280
So don't worry about it.

1135
00:39:51,610 --> 00:39:54,040
In any case, I don't want a stepfather.

1136
00:39:54,130 --> 00:39:55,520
That depends on your mom.

1137
00:39:55,890 --> 00:39:58,130
No, it depends on you.

1138
00:39:59,130 --> 00:40:00,240
Why me?

1139
00:40:00,450 --> 00:40:02,450
Because you must protect Mom.

1140
00:40:02,450 --> 00:40:03,410
Do you understand?

1141
00:40:03,930 --> 00:40:05,040
Are you telling me what to do?

1142
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,930
Because if you get in Mom's way,

1143
00:40:06,930 --> 00:40:09,040
no guys can snatch her away.

1144
00:40:09,040 --> 00:40:09,610
Am I right?

